    </Details></BugPattern><BugPattern abbrev='WMI' category='PERFORMANCE' type='WMI_WRONG_MAP_ITERATOR'><ShortDescription>Inefficient use of keySet iterator instead of entrySet iterator</ShortDescription><Details>

